  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Based on prior findings concerning sleep disturbances, in particular REM sleep disturbances,
      after fast-track hip and knee arthroplasty (H-2-2010-011) we performed a supplemental
      analysis of heart rate variablity after arousals during sleep. We compared preoperative and
      postoperative results.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
